@startuml
title Figure 15. Authentication Activity Diagram
start
:User enters email and password;
:System validates input format;

if (Valid input?) then (Yes)
  :Backend finds account by email;
  if (Account exists and password matches?) then (Yes)
    if (User status is ACTIVE?) then (Yes)
      :Generate access token\nand refresh token;
      :Hash and store refresh token;
      :Return secure cookies / response;
      :Login successful;
      stop
    else (No)
      :Notify account is pending or banned;
      stop
    endif
  else (No)
    :Notify invalid credentials;
    stop
  endif
else (No)
  :Show input validation error;
  stop
endif
@enduml
